name: 1. AU! Is anybody here?
description: Since childhood, I have been madly in love with the forest, I have always been inspired by the beauty of this place, its majesty and constancy. There you can be really alone, alone with your thoughts, isolated from the city noise. Once again inspired by this place, I would like to create a series of several art depicting fictional subjects associated with this miracle of nature. The series will be called "FOREST»
